I3:
- Super+Pause   -   Logout \ Restart \ Shutdown
- Super+c       -   Edit i3 config
- Super+g       -   Show this help
- Super+Shift+c -   Reload configuration file
- Super+Shift+r -   Restart restart i3 inplace (preserves layout/session)
- Super+Shift+e -   Exit i3


Application:
- ctrl+Alt+a    -   Anydesk
- ctrl+Alt+b    -   Behafucha
- ctrl+Alt+c    -   Gnome-calculator
- ctrl+Alt+f    -   Vifm
- ctrl+Alt+g    -   Gimp
- ctrl+Alt+k    -   Keepass
- ctrl+Alt+l    -   Libreoffice writer
- ctrl+Alt+m    -   Kodi
- ctrl+Alt+n    -   Nemo
- ctrl+Alt+r    -   Rofi -show run
- ctrl+Alt+s    -   Rofi -show ssh
- ctrl+Alt+t    -   Thunderbird
- ctrl+Alt+u    -   WhatsApp
- ctrl+Alt+v    -   Virtualbox
- ctrl+Alt+w    -   Firefox
- ctrl+Alt+x    -   xkill
- ctrl+Alt+z    -   Filezilla

Hardware:
- ctrl+Alt+h    -   Refresh hdmi sound
- ctrl+Shift+1  -   Volume Down
- ctrl+Shift+2  -   Volume Up

